01:25.440 --> 01:26.790
with your mouse as well.

01:27.620 --> 01:33.980
Now one really nice feature and Figment are the constraints tools with these tools we can constrain

01:33.980 --> 01:43.850
any objects to the left on top of this our border frame or we can pin it to the right or the center.

01:44.030 --> 01:49.040
