04:51.290 --> 04:53.610
layer Blar or background blur.

04:53.780 --> 05:02.000
Now this background blur is really nice because you have the ability to turn down the opacity and when

05:02.040 --> 05:05.820
to turn this to 70 here so we can kind of see what's going on in the background.

05:05.930 --> 05:11.720
And you can see this layer is blurred the background and these settings can be changed right here.

05:11.720 --> 05:17.920
